description._content: Format: Photograph Find more detailed information about this photograph: acms.sl.nsw.gov.au/item/itemDetailPaged.aspx?itemID=43601 From the collection of the State Library of New South Wales www.sl.nsw.gov.au Stewart House has been there for children in need of health and emotional support for many years. Sadly some of these boys may have been old enough to go to the War ten years from when the photograph was taken, after suffering the problems of the Depression. Stewart House website: www.stewarthouse.org.au/
